dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Terry Martinez. May I have your name, please?
Hello Terry, my name is Linda Turner.
Nice to meet you, Linda. How can I assist you today?
I would like to file a new claim for an accident that occurred last week.
I'm sorry to hear that, Linda. Can you please provide me with the date of the accident in digits?
The accident happened on one two dash zero four dash two zero two two.
Thank you, Linda. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle involved in the accident?
The vehicle is a two zero one nine Toyota Camry.
Great, thank you for the information, Linda. We will begin processing your claim. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help, Terry.
You're welcome, Linda. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
